CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Context Therapeutics Inc. (Nasdaq: CNTX) is a biopharmaceutical company advancing T cell engaging ("TCE") bispecific antibodies for solid tumors. Context is building an innovative portfolio of TCE bispecific therapeutics with multiple products in development, including two clinical-stage assets. Context is headquartered in Philadelphia.
